<p>Land Chain aims to provide a trustworthy real estate ownership record and land registry
system to diminish the financial burden, time invested and land frauds. It will serve as a
foundation for better investments in land, enable the development of a mortgage market and a
credit market in general, and become an institution for trust in one of the most fundamental
parts of an economy: land and real estate.</p><strong><i>Location:</i>Thapar Insititute of Engineering and Technology</strong></p>
